    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The illusion of your Invoke Duplicity has grown more powerful in the following ways.</p><p><strong>Shared Distraction.</strong> When you and your allies make attack rolls against a creature within 5 feet of the illusion, the attack rolls have Advantage.</p><p><strong>Healing Illusion.</strong> When the illusion ends, you or a creature of your choice within 5 feet of it regains a number of Hit Points equal to your Cleric level.</p><section id=\"secret-52OK89KAR0ECC6Re\" class=\"secret\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>Thsi feature includes an activity for the <strong>Healing Illusion</strong> but it does not automate the advantage against creatures within 5 feet of the illusion.</p></section>",
